item.description:
To use the Spring namespace, user need to add the dependency of the elasticjob-spring module in the pom.xml file.
&lt;dependency&gt; &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.shardingsphere.elasticjob&lt;/groupId&gt; &lt;artifactId&gt;elasticjob-spring-namespace&lt;/artifactId&gt; &lt;version&gt;${latest.release.version}&lt;/version&gt; &lt;/dependency&gt; Spring namespace: http://shardingsphere.apache.org/schema/elasticjob/elasticjob.xsd
Registry Center Configuration &lt;elasticjob:zookeeper /&gt;
Configuration:
   Name Required     id Yes   server-lists Yes   namespace Yes   base-sleep-time-milliseconds No   max-sleep-time-milliseconds No   max-retries No   session-timeout-milliseconds No   connection-timeout-milliseconds No   digest No    Job Configuration &lt;elasticjob:job /&gt;
